The paper deals with the problem of designing revenue optimal dynamic mechanisms, which is a topic in game theory (cs.GT) and mechanism design (cs.EC). The use of bank account mechanisms involves the manipulation of real numbers, which suggests a connection to data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the use of randomized and deterministic mechanisms, which are topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
